<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ url_for('static', filename='index.css') }}">
    <title>{{ app_name }} - Homepage</title>
</head>
<body style="background-color: #0C0F15;"></body>
<body>

    <div class="heading">
        <h1 class="title-text-box">{{ app_name }}</h1>
        <p class="title-description">Self-hostable media server</p>
    </div>


    <div class="secondary-box">
        <h1 class="secondary-title">How it works</h1>
        <p class="secondary-text">
            You can upload files to your instance by going to the web gui located at /upload, you can also upload files from a script by sending a post request to /api/upload. We are constantly working on ways to improve this.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="primary-box">
        <h1 class="primary-title">Software Credits</h1>
        <p class="primary-text">
            This server is powered by A3D CDN, a self-hostable media server written in python deployed within 1 minute using docker and docker compose. Check out our repository on github and consider deploying it yourself.
        </p>
    </div>


    <div class="footer">
        <p>Made with ❤️ by Atomic2ds</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>